metadata.name: Starfighter #1
metadata.description: Starfighterclub is a collection of 333 unique starfighters, fully handcrafted by the Italian artist Cesare.studio. All Starfighter holders can participate in exclusive events such as raffles, community giveways and much more, but most importantly, all holders are cool people, because they choose the high quality! Visit https://www.starfighterclub.com/ for more details.
